text: Mariana Isabel Conde (born 23 July 1973) is an Argentine volleyball player. She played at the 2002 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Championship. She played for Volley 2000 Spezzano and Volley Modena. == References == == Other websites == * https://women.volleybox.net/mariana-isabel-conde-p20740 Category:1973 births Category:Argentine volleyball players Category:Living people
